## 8. Prohibited Patterns (V2 — Comprehensive)

- ❌ Do NOT write to `party_documents.file_path`, `file_name`, `file_mime_type`, or `file_size`
- ❌ Do NOT create `*_documents` tables for any ERP module after DMS.6
- ❌ Do NOT store AI API keys in any database column
- ❌ Do NOT add document types to `party_document_types` after DMS.3 — use `dms_document_types`
- ❌ Do NOT reference `party_document_types` in any new form after DMS.6
- ❌ Do NOT call AI provider SDKs directly in DMS feature code — use factory functions
- ❌ Do NOT generate signed URLs in client components — server actions only
- ❌ Do NOT hardcode one AI provider (OpenAI, Azure, etc.) in DMS code
- ❌ Do NOT add `{entity}_id FK` columns to `dms_documents` — use `dms_document_links`
- ❌ Do NOT disable RLS on any DMS table or `erp_ai_provider_configs`
- ❌ Do NOT auto-save AI-extracted values — all go to review queue first
- ❌ Do NOT implement DMS features before Sameer approves DMS.2 phase prompt

